    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        "It is good; faculties are good. They give us knowledge about every area included in the syllabus and make us aware of the topics in it and their importance. Every faculty member was good and excellent in their respective areas.",
        "There was a placement cell in our college that greatly helped in the placement of students.",
        "Post-metric scholarships are provided by the state government every year. A good amount is provided by them that we can use to continue our studies without any problems. The scholarship is provided for every student irrespective of their social status.",
        "It has a basketball court and a football ground accordingly. All the courses have the best lab facilities, including seminar halls. The library is fully equipped with all the books the students require.",
        "In the case of hostels, first look at the hostel room and facilities to determine if they are good or not. Then, assess the surrounding area to see if it is a good location. The food and accommodation should be of good quality and cleanliness. Additionally, ensure that the fan and lights are of good quality.",
        "I have seen so many positive things, including good faculty who have a very high level of knowledge."
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
